title: X-PLANE New York Airports & City XP (Original Files)
description:
New York City XP is a scenery of New York metropolitan area in the United States of America. This scenery is one of the most complex add-ons for flight simulators, featuring 2500 sq km of high resolution terrain with autogen and over 6300 custom-made New York buildings.

New York Airports XP is the most complete, affordable and performance-friendly package on the market containing 6 New York airports - 3 from the largest airport system in the world (KJFK Kennedy, KEWR Newark and KLGA LaGuardia) and 3 business & general aviation airports from the surrounding area (KTEB Teterboro, KCDW Essex County and KLDJ Linden).

These are the original files.

Great scenery's, support the devs, buy them if you like them
